## 1. Authentication

### 🌐 POST `/user-signup`
Register or login via social / phone / email.

**Body (`multipart/form-data`):**
| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|-------|------|----------|-------|
| `type` | string | ✅ | `email` `google` `phone` `apple` |
| `firebase_id` | string | ✅ | Firebase UID |
| `email` | string | — | Required for `email` / `google` |
| `mobile` | string | — | Required for `phone` |
| `country_code` | string | — | e.g. `+977` |
| `name` | string | — | Display name |
| `profile` | file | — | jpg/png max 7 MB |
| `fcm_id` | string | — | Push notification token |
| `platform_type` | string | — | `android` or `ios` |
| `registration` | boolean | — | `true` = skip token creation |

**Response:** user object + `token`

---

### 🌐 GET `/get-otp`
Send OTP to a phone number.

**Query params:** `mobile`, `country_code`

---

### 🌐 GET `/verify-otp`
Verify OTP.

**Query params:** `mobile`, `otp`

---

### 🌐 POST `/forgot-password`
Send a password-reset link.

**Body:** `{ "email": "user@example.com" }`

---

### 🌐 POST `/reset-password`
Reset password using the emailed token.

**Body:** `{ "token": "...", "email": "...", "password": "...", "password_confirmation": "..." }`

---

### 🔒 POST `/logout`
Invalidate the current Bearer token.

---

### 🔒 POST `/switch-role`
Switch between guest / owner roles.

**Body:** `{ "role": "owner" }`

---

