## 10. Nepal Payments — Khalti & eSewa

### 🔒 POST `/payment/khalti/initiate`
👤 Initiate a Khalti payment.

**Body:**
```json
{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "return_url": "https://yourapp.com/payment/callback"
}
```

**Response:** `{ "payment_url": "https://khalti.com/...", "pidx": "..." }`

---

### 🔒 POST `/payment/esewa/initiate`
👤 Initiate an eSewa payment.

**Body:**
```json
{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "success_url": "https://yourapp.com/success",
  "failure_url": "https://yourapp.com/failure"
}
```

**Response:** eSewa form parameters for redirect.

---

### 🌐 GET `/payment/khalti/callback`
Khalti gateway redirect callback — handled automatically.

**Query params:** `pidx`, `status`, `transaction_id`, `booking_id`

---

### 🌐 GET `/payment/esewa/callback`
eSewa success redirect — handled automatically.

---

### 🌐 GET `/payment/esewa/failure`
eSewa failure redirect — handled automatically.

